data.title: Mexico to build Latin America's most powerful 314-petaflop supercomputer
data.description: Mexico announced on Wednesday plans to build Coatlicue, a 314-petaflop supercomputer that will become Latin America's most powerful.
data.author: Sujita Sinha
data.keywords: AI, Artificial Inteligence, Coatlicue, Coatlicue supercomputer, Mexico, supercomputer
